This documentation describes the Guardtime Blockchain Enabled Service Tile for Pivotal Cloud Foundry (PCF). By using the Guardtime Blockchain Enabled Service Tile, applications and application service instances can sign data using Guardtime's Keyless Signature Infrastructure (KSI) that provides cryptographic signatures in real time.

The Guardtime Blockchain Enabled Service Tile registers a service broker on PCF and exposes the Guardtime KSI Access service on the Marketplace. Developers can create service instances of Guardtime KSI Access and bind them to their applications using Apps Manager or the cf Command Line Interface (CLI). Bound applications can sign and verify data using Guardtime KSI.

