## <a id="reqs"></a>Requirements

The Guardtime Blockchain Enabled Service Tile has the following requirements:

* A Guardtime KSI blockchain service endpoint, port, administrator account, and administrator password. See the [License](#license) section below for information about obtaining a Guardtime KSI 60-day free trial.  
* The Redis for PCF tile. The Guardtime Blockchain Enabled Service Tile uses a Redis datastore to hold metadata and binding information. For more information about how to install Redis for PCF, see the [documentation](../redis/index.html).
* A local Redis service in the development environment.

